{"tid":1770690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《打字兼職人員》堅定流？","createTime":"2019-12-05T10:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T10:58:33.000Z","uid":334785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e42546aa5cc51d1ec81d60cd13d2054d7b25f47c","tid":1770690,"uid":334785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"我有位相識好耐的朋友問我對衣份工有無興趣<br />\n<br />\n「香港/中國/台灣<br />\n<br />\n我打算在此外宣一下打字兼職人員。這份工作是你只有手機，在那及任何時候也可以工作。任務多不勝數。想去買昂貴的東西或是去課金但身上沒$就快來賺賺$。只收一次繳付，絕沒多次繳付，真的不是在騙你。有興趣可來私聊」<br />\n<br />\n世上真係有如此便宜的午餐？<br />\n有無人試過？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEOSw5o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEOSw5o.png&h=a491231b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b88165ce72f54159e1778bf368ffd395a074e691","tid":1770690,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">128  維園見</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NubQiBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNubQiBY.jpg&h=92e1c59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmZKn8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmZKn8j.jpg&h=63ee12ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqTnUd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqTnUd9.jpg&h=3e0f0960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ounWYCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FounWYCe.jpg&h=82df0bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsKuy8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsKuy8t.jpg&h=252ad633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42rgYzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li